data.description: Such a cute house on a half acre lot! Many upgrades include new roof, updated AC, flooring in most of the house is the luxury plank tile. Kitchen updated with granite countertops and all appliances stay. Enjoy the convenience to go anywhere in Jacksonville in a matter of minutes. Located on the Southside. Home features a oversized carport No HOA so park your boat or RV here as well. Nice detached shed workshop for all of your hobbies. Formal living room dining room and family room. Arched doorways give all the feel of such a charming space. Easy to show and ready to close Theres fruit trees on the property as well. Applie Lemon and more. Plush landscaping
